#####Configure data source for Linux

1. Start a terminal.
2. Navigate to the Edge System installation directory: /opt/EdgeSystem.
3. To configure a data source, run this command:

   ...
./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource IP=IpAddress Port=TcpPort
   ...

4. To view configured data sources and help, run this command:

   ...
./OSIsoft.Data.System.Host configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource
   ...

